description: Fresh BBQ Innovations is bringing you the newest and tastiest ways to enjoy BBQ in Arizona! With a style all their own, this truck's terrific ideas make the taste of their delicious Sausages, Pulled Pork, and BBQ Wraps truly revolutionary. With their vegetarian and gluten-free options, this truck has something for everyone. Don't miss this chance - grab something delicious from Fresh BBQ Innovations today!
name: Fresh BBQ Innovations
